{"tid":686900,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"女神拍拖既話會唔會unfollow佢？","createTime":"2018-06-01T17:07:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T19:50:14.000Z","uid":14436,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f4ffdf5bdf80f19f684e5b151d2f87a7160e14bb","tid":686900,"uid":14436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T17:07:39.000Z","msg":"如題<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n假設女神平時會經常同你吹水（當然你搵佢多d),甚至會同你單獨出街食飯旅行等等,但佢已經係字裡行間中透露出大家只係好朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有日佢同你講佢拍拖喇, 講完恭喜之後,你會唔會unfollow曬佢所有野,甚至唔再覆佢message,等佢慢慢係自己世界消失?<br />\n<br />\n對唔住毒撚多ff,純粹想叫下春<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"496dba7c0a3da6dcc56b44725445de66ef9602e4","tid":686900,"uid":14436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T17:13:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2387b6d734dc0a20dfb8ea848314056ec10bc42","tid":686900,"uid":81575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T17:18:26.000Z","msg":"條街咁多女，將你心思花係第二個身上啦"},{"pid":"5866ebdc9e01ce2c4b0dd5e8990208484a4293f3","tid":686900,"uid":14436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2387b6d734dc0a20dfb8ea848314056ec10bc42","tid":686900,"uid":81575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T17:18:26.000Z","msg":"條街咁多女，將你心思花係第二個身上啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T17:21:20.000Z","msg":"明白呀巴打,我都想慢慢唔再諗咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a57089917093524d2795d1b9977f7cf4c760e73e","tid":686900,"uid":81575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5866ebdc9e01ce2c4b0dd5e8990208484a4293f3","tid":686900,"uid":14436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2387b6d734dc0a20dfb8ea848314056ec10bc42","tid":686900,"uid":81575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,